# Email Configuration (for OTP)
# The system supports two email sending methods with automatic fallback:
# 1. Resend API (Recommended) - HTTP-based, most reliable in cloud environments
# 2. SMTP (Fallback) - Traditional email protocol (Gmail, etc.)

# ===============================================
# OPTION 1: Resend API (Recommended)
# ===============================================
# ✅ HTTP-based (no firewall/port issues)
# ✅ Fast and reliable
# ✅ Better for production/cloud environments
# ⚠️ Requires domain verification for production use
#
# Setup:
# 1. Sign up at https://resend.com
# 2. Get your API key from https://resend.com/api-keys
# 3. For testing: Use the default "onboarding@resend.dev" sender
# 4. For production: Verify your domain at https://resend.com/domains
#
